{"tid":171052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個的士司機有料","createTime":"2017-03-25T05:17:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-26T06:00:54.000Z","uid":35583,"like":130,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"55bc93b735ee57290aff32f79b8ac0e4b1380464","tid":171052,"uid":35583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T05:17:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170325&amp;guid=56476556&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170325%26guid%3D56476556%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=UyoO8KdNfTPb55o7yEEcozQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=3bd0b2d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170325%26guid%3D56476556%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=09b78fe9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170325&amp;guid=56476556&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n清晨5時許，一名南亞女子在灣仔盧押道截的士往跑馬地，的士沿菲林明道往告士打道方向行駛，其間司機懷疑拒載，打開車門要女乘客下車，雙方發生爭執，女乘客不滿準備打電話報警。<br />\n<br />\n據稱，駛至謝斐道交界時，司機一手搶過女乘客手機掟出車外，並且在路口U TURN急轉彎，將女乘客篩出車外，繼而加速駛走。幸事發時尾隨車輛及時煞停，女乘客僅左膝擦傷。救護員到場替其包紮送院，警方追緝涉案的士司機下落。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70491e7599e80944afdf819fc54e4ff95c698e38","tid":171052,"uid":56878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T05:19:12.000Z","msg":"南亞vs拒載的士佬<br />\n<br />\n我急不及待要好好玩了"},{"pid":"8004a50ce639313a5dd4c18b69eb9fe688471342","tid":171052,"uid":57797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T05:21:54.000Z","msg":"好波！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f72a6e65c5726208e1fb1a75169175855bef85f5","tid":171052,"uid":3549,"like":0